        <Parent_String>Gmelina (genus) [300343891], Lamiaceae (family) [300343893], Lamiales (order) [300343869], Magnoliopsida (class) [300375593], Angiospermae (division) [300265706], Plantae (kingdom) [300132360], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
